<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 06:14:41 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>亚玛芬体育对中国的依赖对 2024 年首次大规模 IPO 构成压力 - 消息人士</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/amer-sports-china-reliance-weighs-2024s-first-big-ipo-sources-2024-01-31/</link><description>四名参与该过程的人士告诉路透社，亚玛芬体育 (Amer Sports) 的收入日益依赖中国，这正在影响那些考虑购买这家运动器材制造商 18 亿美元美国首次公开募股 (IPO) 的投资者的兴趣。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 06:05:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/amer-sports-china-reliance-weighs-2024s-first-big-ipo-sources-2024-01-31/</guid></item><item><title>评级机构：恒大的债券持有人可能要等待数年才能获得微薄的支付</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/evergrandes-bond-holders-could-wait-years-little-payout-ratings-agency-2024-01-31/</link><description>标准普尔全球评级表示，中国恒大的离岸美元债券持有人将在一个复杂的过程中获得潜在的微额支付，该过程在这家房地产巨头进入清算后可能需要数年时间才能完成。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 05:29:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/evergrandes-bond-holders-could-wait-years-little-payout-ratings-agency-2024-01-31/</guid></item><item><title>中国根据“项目白名单”机制发放首笔开发贷款 - 媒体</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-issues-first-development-loan-under-project-whitelist-mechanism-media-2024-01-31/</link><description>据中国官方《证券时报》周三报道，第一笔开发贷款已根据中国所谓的“项目白名单”机制发放。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 05:19:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-issues-first-development-loan-under-project-whitelist-mechanism-media-2024-01-31/</guid></item><item><title>中国主要城市放宽购房限制以促进销售</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinese-major-cities-ease-home-purchase-limits-boost-sales-2024-01-31/</link><description>中国的两个主要城市苏州和上海跟随广州放松了购房限制，以促进房地产销售，因为信心持续疲软阻碍了受危机打击的房地产行业的复苏。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 05:00:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinese-major-cities-ease-home-purchase-limits-boost-sales-2024-01-31/</guid></item><item><title>台湾总统告诉教皇方济各，她支持他对人工智能的担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-president-tells-pope-francis-she-supports-his-ai-concerns-2024-01-31/</link><description>台湾总统蔡英文已致信教皇方济各，支持他对人工智能使用的担忧，并承诺与台湾唯一的欧洲盟友进行更深入的合作。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 04:33:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-president-tells-pope-francis-she-supports-his-ai-concerns-2024-01-31/</guid></item><item><title>中国称激怒台湾的气球“不是什么新鲜事”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-balloons-that-have-angered-taiwan-are-nothing-new-2024-01-31/</link><description>中国政府周三驳回了台湾多次对中国热气球飞越或靠近该岛的抱怨，称这些热气球是出于气象目的，不应出于政治原因大肆宣传。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 04:11:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-balloons-that-have-angered-taiwan-are-nothing-new-2024-01-31/</guid></item><item><title>中国对南海黄岩岛拥有无可争辩的主权-海岸警卫队</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-has-indisputable-sovereignty-over-scarborough-shoal-south-china-sea-coast-2024-01-31/</link><description>中国海警发言人周二晚间发表声明称，中国对黄岩岛及其附近海域拥有无可争辩的主权，对菲律宾的侵犯行为一贯予以坚决反击。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 03:25:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-has-indisputable-sovereignty-over-scarborough-shoal-south-china-sea-coast-2024-01-31/</guid></item><item><title>美国官员表示，太平洋岛屿需要加强数字安全才能加入海底电缆</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pacific-islands-need-boost-digital-security-join-undersea-cable-says-us-official-2024-01-31/</link><description>美国国务院一位高级官员表示，想要连接美国资助的海底电缆的太平洋岛屿国家需要确保其数字生态系统的安全，以防范来自中国的数据风险。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 03:17:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pacific-islands-need-boost-digital-security-join-undersea-cable-says-us-official-2024-01-31/</guid></item><item><title>由于中国经济拖累，亚洲股市月度下跌；联邦公开市场委员会迫在眉睫</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-01-31/</link><description>亚洲股市周三普遍下跌，而澳元下跌，原因是国内通胀数据出人意​​料地疲弱，且短期国债收益率在美联储利率决定前保持高位。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 02:34:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-01-31/</guid></item><item><title>国际货币基金组织认为亚洲有降息空间，敦促中国明确房地产修复措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/imf-sees-improved-prospects-soft-landing-asian-economies-2024-01-31/</link><description>国际货币基金组织周三表示，随着通胀放缓，亚洲央行可能会在今年晚些时候看到放松货币政策的空间，并呼吁中国就计划如何解决房地产问题发出明确信息。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 02:19:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/imf-sees-improved-prospects-soft-landing-asian-economies-2024-01-31/</guid></item><item><title>中国数据疲弱，油价下跌；预计自 9 月以来首次月度上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-ticks-down-asian-trade-despite-rising-middle-east-tensions-2024-01-31/</link><description>周三，全球最大原油进口国中国经济数据低迷，打压了需求情绪，油价下跌，但由于中东冲突扩大引发了供应担忧，油价预计将出现 9 月份以来的首次月度上涨。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 02:11:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-ticks-down-asian-trade-despite-rising-middle-east-tensions-2024-01-31/</guid></item><item><title>中国工厂活动再度萎缩，需求疲软拖累经济</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-factory-activity-shrinks-again-jan-demand-still-weak-2024-01-31/</link><description>周三的官方工厂调查显示，中国 1 月份制造业活动连续第四个月萎缩，这表明庞大的行业和更广泛的经济在 2024 年初难以恢复增长势头。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 02:07:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-factory-activity-shrinks-again-jan-demand-still-weak-2024-01-31/</guid></item><item><title>大雾导致中国港口暂停航运；上海发布加强咨询</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/heavy-fog-suspends-shipping-chinese-ports-shanghai-issues-heightened-advisory-2024-01-31/</link><description>据中国官方媒体周三报道，大雾导致穿越中国广东省沿海琼州海峡的船只暂停航行，包括上海在内的多个城市已发布警告公告。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 01:46:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/heavy-fog-suspends-shipping-chinese-ports-shanghai-issues-heightened-advisory-2024-01-31/</guid></item><item><title>新西兰外长：美国需要在太平洋地区加强合作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-needs-work-with-greater-intensity-pacific-nz-min-2024-01-31/</link><description>新西兰外交部长温斯顿·彼得斯表示，新西兰将于周三开始与澳大利亚就与 AUKUS 三边防务伙伴关系的合作进行谈判，并补充说华盛顿需要在太平洋地区采取更多行动，以对抗那里的其他政治影响。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 01:03:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-needs-work-with-greater-intensity-pacific-nz-min-2024-01-31/</guid></item><item><title>市场关注美联储，美元有望月度上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-eyes-monthly-gain-markets-look-fed-2024-01-31/</link><description>周三，美元创九月以来最大月度涨幅，日元创近一年来最大跌幅，交易员等待美国一月份利率决定。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 00:50:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-eyes-monthly-gain-markets-look-fed-2024-01-31/</guid></item></channel></rss>